### ============================================================
### AWARD NOMINEES API REQUESTS
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000/v1/nominees
### ============================================================

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@awardId = 1
@categoryId = 1
@nomineeId = 1

### ============================================================
### PUBLIC ROUTES (No Authentication Required)
### ============================================================

### List Nominees by Category
# Query Params: ?include_stats=true|false
GET {{baseUrl}}/nominees/award-categories/{{categoryId}}?include_stats=true

